    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="backgroundMode" id="0ff16f2b-72fa-499b-a921-f682ab158a2c">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>This is for determining the appropriate mask at run time,
for example, the std behaviour in real_mode is to only display
planned containers in the background. The problem is where there
are QUEUED containers as well.
This gives the ability to adjust the background display mode
accordingly. If set to queue_mode, then we display queued in 
background.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
